minios-dracut (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Add mkdracut script for building MiniOS initramfs
  * Add 90minios dracut module with MiniOS-specific initialization
  * Add 99minios-cleanup dracut module
  * Add dracut configuration files (90-minios.conf)
  * Include static binaries (busybox, blkid, mount helpers, etc.)
  * Include livekitlib library for live system functionality
  * Self-contained package with all required dependencies

